<template>
  <el-form
    size="medium"
    label-position="right"
    label-width="auto"
    ref="relaElForm"
    style="margin-left: 24px;"
  >
    <el-row :gutter="10">
      <el-col :span=7 v-for="(item,index) in elementDatas">
        <el-form-item :label="item.label" :required="item.required">
          <!--日期-->
          <el-date-picker value-format="yyyy-MM-dd" v-if="item.type === 'date'" clearable :disabled="item.disabled"
                          :readonly="item.readonly"
                          :placeholder="item.placeholder" v-model="item.config.defaultValue"/>
          <!--下拉选-->
          <el-select v-if="item.type === 'select'" :disabled="item.disabled" :readonly="item.readonly"
                     clearable
                     :placeholder="item.placeholder" :multiple="item.multiple" v-model="item.config.defaultValue">
            <el-option v-for="(sItem,sIndex) in item.slot.options"
                       :key="sIndex"
                       :label="sItem.label"
                       :value="sItem.value">
            </el-option>
          </el-select>
          <!--文本域-->
          <el-input v-if="item.type === 'textarea'" clearable type="textarea" :disabled="item.disabled"
                    :readonly="item.readonly"
                    v-model="item.config.defaultValue" :placeholder="item.placeholder"/>

          <!--文本框-->
          <el-input v-if="item.type === 'text'" type="text" clearable :disabled="item.disabled"
                    :readonly="item.readonly"
                    v-model="item.config.defaultValue" :placeholder="item.placeholder"/>

          <!--复选框-->
          <el-checkbox-group v-if="item.type === 'checkbox'" :disabled="item.disabled"
                             :readonly="item.readonly" v-model="item.config.defaultValue"
                             :placeholder="item.placeholder">
            <el-checkbox v-for="(cItem,cIndex) in item.slot.options"
                         :label="cItem.label" :value="cItem.value"/>
          </el-checkbox-group>

          <!--单选框-->
          <el-radio-group v-if="item.type === 'radio'" :disabled="item.disabled" :readonly="item.readonly"
                          v-model="item.config.defaultValue"
                          :placeholder="item.placeholder">
            <el-radio v-for="(rItem,rIndex) in item.slot.options" :key="rIndex"
                      :label="rItem.value" :value="rItem.value">{{ rItem.label }}
            </el-radio>
          </el-radio-group>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-col>
    </el-row>
  </el-form>
</template>
<script>

  export default {
    name: 'custompage',
    props: {
      elementDatas: {
        required: true,
        type: Array
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {}
    },
    computed: {},
    mounted() {
    },
    watch: {
      'elementDatas': {
        handler: function (newV, oldV) {
          let pdInfo = this.getJsonData('pdTestInfo')
          console.log(pdInfo)
          newV.forEach(ele => {
            if (ele.vModel == "productName") {
              ele.disabled = true;
              ele.config.defaultValue = pdInfo.pdName
            }
            if (ele.vModel == "Insurance Code") {
              ele.disabled = true;
              ele.config.defaultValue = pdInfo.pdCode
            }
            if (ele.vModel == "Insurance Version") {
              ele.disabled = true;
              console.log(ele.config.defaultValue)
              if (ele.config.defaultValue == null || ele.config.defaultValue == "") {
                ele.config.defaultValue = pdInfo.pdVerId
              }
            }
          })
        },
        deep: true,
        immediate: true

      }
    },
    created() {
    },
    methods: {}
  }
</script>
<style lang="scss" scoped>


</style>
